
    NYPD hunt couple who lost ring during romantic proposal

        

    
        
                
                Image copyright
                  NYPD
                
            
            
        Police in New York are hunting a couple who got engaged in Times Square on Friday but lost the ring down a grate.CCTV images show the romantic proposal going wrong and the pair unsuccessfully trying to retrieve the piece of jewellery.After seeing the footage officers managed to rescue the ring, clean it up and now want to find its owners.They have put out a plea for the man and woman to come forward.
    
        
